---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Smart Home Cost Calculator UK 2025 — How Much Does It Cost?"
  description="Use our free smart home cost calculator to estimate how much it costs to set up a smart home in the UK. Get product recommendations and Amazon affiliate links."
  canonicalPath="/smart-home-calculator/"
>

<section class="calc-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="calc-eyebrow">Free tool</p>
    <h1>Smart Home Cost Calculator UK 2025</h1>
    <p class="calc-subtitle">How much does a smart home cost? Select your rooms and devices below to get an instant estimate — with product recommendations and shopping links.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="calc-body">
  <div class="container calc-grid">

    <!-- LEFT: Inputs -->
    <div class="calc-inputs">

      <div class="calc-card">
        <h2>1. Select your rooms</h2>
        <p class="calc-hint">Pick every room you want to make smart.</p>
        <div class="room-grid" id="room-grid">
          <label class="room-btn"><input type="checkbox" name="room" value="living-room" /> <span>🛋️ Living Room</span></label>
          <label class="room-btn"><input type="checkbox" name="room" value="kitchen" /> <span>🍳 Kitchen</span></label>
          <label class="room-btn"><input type="checkbox" name="room" value="bedroom" /> <span>🛏️ Bedroom</span></label>
          <label class="room-btn"><input type="checkbox" name="room" value="bathroom" /> <span>🚿 Bathroom</span></label>
          <label class="room-btn"><input type="checkbox" name="room" value="garden" /> <span>🌿 Garden</span></label>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="calc-card">
        <h2>2. Choose device types</h2>
        <p class="calc-hint">Select every device category you're interested in.</p>
        <div class="device-list" id="device-list">
          <label class="device-item"><input type="checkbox" name="device" value="bulbs" /> <span class="device-label"><strong>💡 Smart Bulbs</strong><small>Colour-changing or white ambiance lighting</small></span></label>
          <label class="device-item"><input type="checkbox" name="device" value="plugs" /> <span class="device-label"><strong>🔌 Smart Plugs</strong><small>Control any appliance remotely</small></span></label>
          <label class="device-item"><input type="checkbox" name="device" value="sensors" /> <span class="device-label"><strong>👁️ Motion Sensors</strong><small>Trigger automations or alerts</small></span></label>
          <label class="device-item"><input type="checkbox" name="device" value="cameras" /> <span class="device-label"><strong>📷 Security Cameras</strong><small>Indoor/outdoor monitoring</small></span></label>
          <label class="device-item"><input type="checkbox" name="device" value="speakers" /> <span class="device-label"><strong>🔊 Smart Speakers</strong><small>Voice control hub for your home</small></span></label>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="calc-card">
        <h2>3. Budget tier</h2>
        <p class="calc-hint">What's your approach?</p>
        <div class="tier-group" id="tier-group">
          <label class="tier-btn"><input type="radio" name="tier" value="budget" checked /> <span><strong>💚 Budget</strong> — Best value picks (IKEA, own-brand)</span></label>
          <label class="tier-btn"><input type="radio" name="tier" value="mid" /> <span><strong>🔵 Mid-range</strong> — Reliable brands (TP-Link, Aqara)</span></label>
          <label class="tier-btn"><input type="radio" name="tier" value="premium" /> <span><strong>🟡 Premium</strong> — Best-in-class (Philips Hue, Nest)</span></label>
        </div>
      </div>

      <button class="btn btn-primary btn-calc" id="calc-btn">Calculate my smart home cost →</button>
    </div>

    <!-- RIGHT: Results -->
    <div class="calc-results" id="calc-results" aria-live="polite">
      <div class="results-placeholder">
        <p>👆 Select your rooms and devices, then hit <strong>Calculate</strong> to see your estimate.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<!-- Internal links / context -->
<section class="calc-context">
  <div class="container prose-section">
    <h2>What does a smart home cost in the UK?</h2>
    <p>The cost of a smart home in the UK varies enormously depending on the number of rooms, device types, and brands you choose. A single-room starter setup with a smart speaker and a couple of bulbs might cost as little as <strong>£30–£50</strong>, while a fully-automated multi-room home with cameras, sensors, and voice control can easily run to <strong>£500–£1,500+</strong>.</p>
    <p>The calculator above gives you a realistic estimate based on actual UK retail prices as of 2025. All product links use the Amazon UK affiliate tag <em>filce-21</em> and help support this site at no extra cost to you.</p>

    <h2>Do I need a smart home hub?</h2>
    <p>Many modern devices (Amazon Echo, Google Nest, Apple HomePod mini) act as hubs themselves. For more advanced automations, <a href="/posts/home-assistant-guide/">Home Assistant is the open-source powerhouse</a> that ties everything together — including cameras, sensors, and third-party devices.</p>

    <h2>What about security cameras?</h2>
    <p>We've tested several UK-friendly options. Read our full <a href="/posts/best-pet-monitoring-cameras-uk-2025/">best pet monitoring cameras UK 2025 guide</a> for detailed recommendations — including outdoor and indoor options that work with Home Assistant.</p>

    <div class="cta-box">
      <p>🏠 <strong>Want the full smart home setup guide?</strong></p>
      <p>Our in-depth PDF guide covers wiring, automations, Home Assistant config, and affiliate product picks — all tailored for UK homes.</p>
      <a href="https://gumroad.com/l/ai-home-assistant-guide" class="btn btn-primary" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Get the guide →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
.calc-hero {
  background: var(--color-accent-light);
  padding: 3rem 0 2rem;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
}
.calc-eyebrow {
  text-transform: uppercase;
  font-size: var(--size-xs);
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  color: var(--color-accent);
  font-weight: 600;
  margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
}
.calc-hero h1 {
  font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 4vw, 2.4rem);
  line-height: 1.2;
  margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
}
.calc-subtitle {
  color: var(--color-text-muted);
  max-width: 640px;
  font-size: var(--size-lg);
}

.calc-body { padding: 2.5rem 0; }

.calc-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 2rem;
  align-items: start;
}
@media (max-width: 760px) {
  .calc-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
}

.calc-card {
  background: var(--color-bg-alt);
  border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  padding: 1.5rem;
  margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
}
.calc-card h2 {
  font-size: var(--size-xl);
  margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
}
.calc-hint {
  font-size: var(--size-sm);
  color: var(--color-text-muted);
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

/* Rooms */
.room-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(140px, 1fr));
  gap: 0.6rem;
}
.room-btn {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0.5rem;
  background: var(--color-bg);
  border: 2px solid var(--color-border);
  border-radius: var(--radius);
  padding: 0.6rem 0.8rem;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: border-color 0.15s, background 0.15s;
  font-size: var(--size-sm);
}
.room-btn input { display: none; }
.room-btn:has(input:checked) {
  border-color: var(--color-accent);
  background: var(--color-accent-light);
  color: var(--color-accent);
  font-weight: 600;
}

/* Devices */
.device-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.6rem; }
.device-item {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0.75rem;
  background: var(--color-bg);
  border: 2px solid var(--color-border);
  border-radius: var(--radius);
  padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: border-color 0.15s, background 0.15s;
}
.device-item input { display: none; }
.device-item:has(input:checked) {
  border-color: var(--color-accent);
  background: var(--color-accent-light);
}
.device-label { display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
.device-label strong { font-size: var(--size-base); }
.device-label small { color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: var(--size-xs); margin-top: 2px; }
.device-item:has(input:checked) .device-label small { color: var(--color-accent); }

/* Tiers */
.tier-group { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem; }
.tier-btn {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0.75rem;
  background: var(--color-bg);
  border: 2px solid var(--color-border);
  border-radius: var(--radius);
  padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: border-color 0.15s, background 0.15s;
  font-size: var(--size-sm);
}
.tier-btn input { display: none; }
.tier-btn:has(input:checked) {
  border-color: var(--color-accent);
  background: var(--color-accent-light);
  font-weight: 600;
}

.btn-calc {
  width: 100%;
  padding: 0.9rem;
  font-size: var(--size-lg);
  border: none;
  cursor: pointer;
}

/* Results panel */
.calc-results {
  position: sticky;
  top: 5rem;
  background: var(--color-surface);
  border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
  padding: 1.75rem;
  min-height: 300px;
}
.results-placeholder {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  min-height: 200px;
  text-align: center;
  color: var(--color-text-muted);
  font-size: var(--size-lg);
  line-height: 1.5;
}

/* Result content styles (injected by JS) */
.result-estimate {
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}
.result-estimate h3 { font-size: var(--size-xl); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
.cost-range {
  display: flex;
  gap: 0.75rem;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
}
.cost-badge {
  padding: 0.4rem 1rem;
  border-radius: var(--radius);
  font-weight: 700;
  font-size: var(--size-2xl);
}
.cost-badge.low { background: #dcfce7; color: #166534; }
.cost-badge.high { background: #fef9c3; color: #854d0e; }
@media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
  .cost-badge.low { background: #14532d; color: #86efac; }
  .cost-badge.high { background: #422006; color: #fde68a; }
}
.result-products h3 { font-size: var(--size-xl); margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
.product-list { list-style: none; padding: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.6rem; }
.product-list li {
  background: var(--color-bg);
  border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  border-radius: var(--radius);
  padding: 0.6rem 0.9rem;
  font-size: var(--size-sm);
}
.product-list li a { font-weight: 600; }
.product-list li .prod-price { color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: var(--size-xs); display: block; margin-top: 2px; }
.result-disclaimer {
  margin-top: 1rem;
  font-size: var(--size-xs);
  color: var(--color-text-faint);
  border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  padding-top: 0.75rem;
}

/* Context section */
.calc-context { padding: 2.5rem 0 3rem; background: var(--color-bg-alt); border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
.prose-section { max-width: var(--container-prose); }
.prose-section h2 { font-size: var(--size-2xl); margin: 1.75rem 0 0.6rem; }
.prose-section h2:first-child { margin-top: 0; }
.prose-section p { color: var(--color-text-muted); margin-bottom: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; }
.cta-box {
  background: var(--color-accent-light);
  border: 1px solid var(--color-accent);
  border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  padding: 1.5rem;
  margin-top: 2rem;
}
.cta-box p { color: var(--color-text); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
.cta-box .btn { margin-top: 0.75rem; }
</style>

<script>
const PRODUCTS = {
  bulbs: {
    budget: { name: 'IKEA TRADFRI Smart Bulb E27', price: '£8–£15 each', url: 'https://www.amazon.co.uk/s?k=IKEA+TRADFRI+smart+bulb&tag=filce-21' },
    mid:    { name: 'TP-Link Tapo L530E Smart Bulb', price: '£12–£18 each', url: 'https://www.amazon.co.uk/s?k=TP-Link+Tapo+L530E&tag=filce-21' },
    premium:{ name: 'Philips Hue White & Colour Ambiance', price: '£35–£55 each', url: 'https://www.amazon.co.uk/s?k=Philips+Hue+White+Colour+Ambiance+E27&tag=filce-21' },
    unitLow: 8, unitHigh: 55
  },
  plugs: {
    budget: { name: 'Amazon Smart Plug (Alexa)', price: '£12–£15 each', url: 'https://www.amazon.co.uk/s?k=amazon+smart+plug&tag=filce-21' },
    mid:    { name: 'TP-Link Tapo P110 Smart Plug', price: '£15–£20 each', url: 'https://www.amazon.co.uk/s?k=TP-Link+Tapo+P110&tag=filce-21' },
    premium:{ name: 'TP-Link Kasa EP25 Energy Monitoring Plug', price: '£20–£28 each', url: 'https://www.amazon.co.uk/s?k=TP-Link+Kasa+EP25&tag=filce-21' },
    unitLow: 12, unitHigh: 28
  },
  sensors: {
    budget: { name: 'Sonoff SNZB-03 Motion Sensor', price: '£10–£15 each', url: 'https://www.amazon.co.uk/s?k=Sonoff+SNZB-03+motion+sensor&tag=filce-21' },
    mid:    { name: 'Aqara Motion Sensor P1', price: '£20–£28 each', url: 'https://www.amazon.co.uk/s?k=Aqara+motion+sensor+P1&tag=filce-21' },
    premium:{ name: 'Philips Hue Motion Sensor', price: '£35–£45 each', url: 'https://www.amazon.co.uk/s?k=Philips+Hue+Motion+Sensor&tag=filce-21' },
    unitLow: 10, unitHigh: 45
  },
  cameras: {
    budget: { name: 'Reolink E1 Pro Indoor Camera', price: '£25–£40', url: 'https://www.amazon.co.uk/s?k=Reolink+E1+Pro&tag=filce-21' },
    mid:    { name: 'Reolink Argus 3 Pro Outdoor Camera', price: '£60–£90', url: 'https://www.amazon.co.uk/s?k=Reolink+Argus+3+Pro&tag=filce-21' },
    premium:{ name: 'Reolink RLC-810A PoE Camera', price: '£80–£120', url: 'https://www.amazon.co.uk/s?k=Reolink+RLC-810A&tag=filce-21' },
    reviewUrl: 'https://filce.uk/posts/reolink-fisheye-camera-review/',
    unitLow: 25, unitHigh: 120
  },
  speakers: {
    budget: { name: 'Amazon Echo Dot (5th Gen)', price: '£35–£55', url: 'https://www.amazon.co.uk/s?k=Amazon+Echo+Dot+5th+gen&tag=filce-21' },
    mid:    { name: 'Amazon Echo (4th Gen)', price: '£70–£90', url: 'https://www.amazon.co.uk/s?k=Amazon+Echo+4th+gen&tag=filce-21' },
    premium:{ name: 'Amazon Echo Studio', price: '£150–£200', url: 'https://www.amazon.co.uk/s?k=Amazon+Echo+Studio&tag=filce-21' },
    unitLow: 35, unitHigh: 200
  }
};

// Multiplier per room (some devices make sense per-room, others once)
const ROOM_MULTIPLIERS = {
  bulbs: true,   // multiply by rooms
  plugs: true,
  sensors: true,
  cameras: true,
  speakers: false // typically one or two, not per-room
};

document.getElementById('calc-btn').addEventListener('click', () => {
  const rooms = [...document.querySelectorAll('input[name="room"]:checked')].map(i => i.value);
  const devices = [...document.querySelectorAll('input[name="device"]:checked')].map(i => i.value);
  const tier = document.querySelector('input[name="tier"]:checked').value;

  if (!rooms.length || !devices.length) {
    document.getElementById('calc-results').innerHTML = `
      <div class="results-placeholder"><p>⚠️ Please select at least one room and one device type.</p></div>`;
    return;
  }

  let totalLow = 0, totalHigh = 0;
  const items = [];

  for (const dev of devices) {
    const data = PRODUCTS[dev];
    const prod = data[tier];
    const qty = ROOM_MULTIPLIERS[dev] ? rooms.length : 1;
    const low = data.unitLow * qty;
    const high = data.unitHigh * qty;
    totalLow += low;
    totalHigh += high;

    let extra = '';
    if (dev === 'cameras' && data.reviewUrl) {
      extra = ` · <a href="${data.reviewUrl}" rel="noopener">Read our camera review</a>`;
    }

    items.push(`
      <li>
        <a href="${prod.url}" rel="sponsored noopener" target="_blank">${prod.name}</a>
        <span class="prod-price">${prod.price} · qty: ${qty}${extra}</span>
      </li>`);
  }

  const roomLabel = rooms.length === 1 ? '1 room' : `${rooms.length} rooms`;

  document.getElementById('calc-results').innerHTML = `
    <div class="result-estimate">
      <h3>💰 Your estimate</h3>
      <p style="color:var(--color-text-muted);font-size:var(--size-sm);margin-bottom:.75rem">${roomLabel} · ${devices.length} device type${devices.length > 1 ? 's' : ''} · ${tier} tier</p>
      <div class="cost-range">
        <span class="cost-badge low">From £${totalLow}</span>
        <span style="align-self:center;color:var(--color-text-muted)">to</span>
        <span class="cost-badge high">Up to £${totalHigh}</span>
      </div>
      <p style="color:var(--color-text-muted);font-size:var(--size-sm)">Estimate based on typical UK retail prices, mid-2025.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="result-products">
      <h3>🛒 Your shopping list</h3>
      <ul class="product-list">${items.join('')}</ul>
    </div>
    <p class="result-disclaimer">As an Amazon Associate I earn from qualifying purchases. Prices are estimates and may vary. Links open Amazon UK with affiliate tag filce-21.</p>
  `;
});
</script>

</BaseLayout>
